  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-stellar\">biomechanical construct</span>, created to the design of an anonymous host.<br><br>Capsules of genetic material, encased in a film of living glass. Shared memories swim in the their reflective surfaces, waiting for their chance to shape the life within.",
